1133
01:37:45,869 --> 01:37:47,069
I know.

1134
01:37:55,970 --> 01:37:59,000
Would you like me to come back?

1135
01:38:10,971 --> 01:38:12,871
Yes.

1136
01:38:13,272 --> 01:38:14,872
Would you?

1137
01:38:16,373 --> 01:38:17,873
Of course.

1138
01:38:19,174 --> 01:38:20,674
