and ah...

1142
01:38:54,577 --> 01:38:56,178
What did he say?

1143
01:38:56,278 --> 01:38:57,278
"Hello"

1144
01:38:57,679 --> 01:39:01,679
"Hello", that's what he says. Just 
"hello", all the time.

1145
01:39:01,880 --> 01:39:03,680
